    | A | C | G | N | S | R | T |
 ___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|
 H1 | a |   | a | A |   |   | a |
 ___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|
 H2 | a |   | A | a |   |   | a |
 ___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|
 H3 |   | a |   |   | a | a | a |
 ___|___|___|___|___|___|___|___|  <------ stratna



--------- 8.4.6. -----------
